    • The Communist Party of India (MarxistLeninist) was formed by the All India Coordination Committee of Communist Revolutionaries (AICCCR) at a congress in Calcutta in 1969. The foundation of the party was declared by Kanu Sanyal at a mass meeting in Calcutta on 22 April (Lenin's birthday).

      Communist Party of India (MarxistLeninist)
      Founder Charu Majumdar, Kanu Sanyal
      Founded 22 April 1969
      Dissolved 31 July 1972
      Ideology Marxism-Leninism

    Meaning :-- I have created the Four Varnas as based on the Gunas and Karmas of the a person in hls last birth. I am their Creator as well as I being Unexpendable i.e. I am no    t their Creator also.
    Comment :-- From the above five verses I hope it will be clear to you Sir that a Brahman's son may not be a Brahman. Though this is laid down by Lord ShriKrushna the so called Brahmans in the past called themselves as Brahmans only because they were born to Brahma parents. Sir a Brahman can be recognised only from his Qualities and not by his family of birth.
    2. I will prove this by quoting the example of Bajirav Peshave no.1. He wanted to do the VrataBandha Vidhi of his son Samsher Bahaddar the son of Mastani. He said I am a Brahman so my son is also a Brahman. But the Brahmans from Pune objected saying how could the son of a Muslim Lady be a Brahman? Sir these so called Brahmans just did not understand that God makes no difference between Hindus and Muslims because He has not said in the Geeta anything about the so called and externally taken man made Religions of people. He makes no difference as based on Religions. So please rethink about all that you have written. Thanking you Sir

    • Dear Sir Namaskar
      1. If you believe in Lord ShriKrushna and the Geeta then you have to accept z
      His authority. He has very clearly told that Varna of a person has nothing whatsoever to do with the Varnas of his parents. If you don't accept this even then there is no problem for me. Because your nonacceptance of Lord ShriKrushna's authority too is caused by Him only. If you are interested in the reason for this kindly refer to the 26th verse of the 7th Ch. of the Geeta given below
      /
      //26//.7.
      Meaning :-- O Arjun ! I know all people who lived in the entire past. Then I also know all who are right now Living all over the world. Further I also know all who will be born in the entire future. But nobody knows Me.
      Comment :-- So since Lord ShriKrushna says " I know all people who will be born in the entire future, and MahaBharat war took place 7576 years back, our present period is the Future period of that MahaBharat period. When He says I know people it means He knows everything about them. So by applying this verse to our this communication, you will find that Lord ShriKrushna knew years back even before our births here that we will be communicating as we are doing today. He knew every word of our communication. Then by applying simple Logic we can say that what we are doing today is what He planned for us to do. That means it was Destined by Lord ShriKrushna for us to do. So if you don't accept whatever the Geeta has told then that also was known to Lord ShriKrushna thousands of years back because He only decided that you will not accept it. That is Destiny or the real Secret of the Geeta. Thanking you Sir
